{"tid":1400456,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急] 如何令狗隻家暴同分化","createTime":"2019-08-03T12:59:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T02:54:22.000Z","uid":112528,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6f2b2e8ea6222c60fd233ff22b7bd689c0ce4edf","tid":1400456,"uid":112528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T12:59:32.000Z","msg":"幫朋友post。<br />\n<br />\n我地唔係要做軍師，但眼見好多巴絲去發夢之後俾人拉真係好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以我地有少少提議，希望勇武巴絲同和理非巴絲都可以一齊討論一下下一步我地點部處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n//首先，my friend, be water 一次，可以嗎？<br />\n<br />\n各位發夢佔領緊彌敦道既手足，懇請真的be water 一次，可以嗎？<br />\n依家個運動無可否認已經係樽頸位，大家都好想有實質成果，所以我地呢邊行動升級，d狗亦會好自然地相應裝備升級。<br />\n<br />\n佔領大馬路、陣地戰、中上環/元朗/旺角巷戰、商場撚狗，除左水戰未打過之外，差唔多邊度都夢遊過。平心而論，除左可以係沙田撚過幾隻落單狗，同狗隻戰術錯誤導致可以兩邊俾人高空進擊外，真係無咩邊次係有優勢。<br />\n依家d狗仲不斷用我地納稅人的錢upgrade裝備，過期催淚彈、海綿彈、橡膠子彈、布袋彈、whatever you name it，遲d仲有水炮車。呢d裝備全部都可以保持人狗距離，所以我地可以撚狗既機會只會愈黎愈細。而且，依家俾親d狗咬住，最低門檻已經係暴動罪，做衝衝仔既成本真係好高好高好高。<br />\n<br />\n因此，my friend, 真的be water，可以嗎？<br />\n<br />\n由於hierarchy 問題，D狗最花時間/精力就係部署戰術同安排狗隻落場，一上親gear之前都肯定要搞一大輪，仲要係每次轉親夢境，佢地都要重新諗過點樣安置d狗。<br />\n所以最理想既情況係：我地不斷游擊，d狗一上gear落場，我地就即刻be water：See you next time, doggie。咁樣就可以浪費晒佢d時間/精力，谷撚晒d精上腦以為可以瘋狗症發作，最後有火無得出，仲要走黎走去咁谷住谷住返狗屋。過多排就肯定會唔耐煩，一係就家暴，一係就自我分化，最後狗咬狗骨。<br />\n<br />\n咁樣先係最低成本既夢遊，be water, my friend, ok?//"},{"pid":"1922b06d1f2d85f3c3bafdb703055ce12db5217c","tid":1400456,"uid":216390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:00:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />be water!!!"},{"pid":"6cb0f9e15cbe55c58e50ef8b8e081be2b61f4ae7","tid":1400456,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T13:09:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆 不分化<br />\n明白大家唔同意見<br />\n呢篇野原意唔係反港獨<br />\n而係希望大家集中翻五大訴求</span></span><br />\n港獨？小心啲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1400357\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1400357</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e8688ca57d35a32b14ac6ed57b043499229eaa99","tid":1400456,"uid":112528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:44:07.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"2f1b79900062183da6afc03055612612172d8ed7","tid":1400456,"uid":112528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T01:55:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86a5d4fec38ae8db6b76cc31b0ecd6ee854e776f","tid":1400456,"uid":59447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:51:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幫推"},{"pid":"8fa2ac5e2669c86527a738bf28d63a0f3f7c36a9","tid":1400456,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:54:22.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><br />\n求下你地青年人 唔好再玩火 香港唔值得要你地禁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不犧牲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不玩火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不篤灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不割席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不指責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[Be fire, my foe] 攬炒戰術？</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nx22GfM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnx22GfM.png&h=e601a00b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jwkf1fN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjwkf1fN.png&h=c4b0c622&s={SIZE}\" /><br /